Manual Test Cases

TC ID: TC_TRAFFIC_001
Title: Verify traffic is not displayed before zoom 2 and is displayed from zoom 2 to zoom 19
Preconditions:
- User can access the traffic-color URL.
- Browser has internet access.
- Martin source is selected with Review tile endpoint.
Steps:
1. Open the URL with zoom 0 and observe traffic layer.
2. Open the URL with zoom 1 and observe traffic layer.
3. Open the URL with zoom 2 and observe traffic layer.
4. Open the URL with zoom 19 and observe traffic layer.
Expected Result:
- Zoom 0: traffic data is not displayed.
- Zoom 1: traffic data is not displayed.
- Zoom 2: traffic data is displayed.
- Zoom 19: traffic data is displayed.
Priority: High


TC ID: TC_TRAFFIC_002
Title: Verify Black, Red, and Orange traffic colors are present
Preconditions:
- User can access the traffic-color URL.
- Martin source is selected with Review tile endpoint.
- Zoom is in visible traffic range (example: zoom 9).
Steps:
1. Open the map at zoom level 9 in Paris area.
2. Ensure review traffic tiles are loaded.
3. Inspect loaded traffic features.
Expected Result:
- Black traffic color is present.
- Red traffic color is present.
- Orange traffic color is present.
Priority: High


